      <hedline>
        <hl1>The Stiff Guy vs. The Dumb Guy</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>What is sad is the smugness of the comedy writers. In the midst of congratulating themselves on their political acuity, they fail to recognize that the left has become the establishment and that the bold role they have assumed is less that of irreverent jester than toady.</p>
        <p>Michael S. Wade  Phoenix</p>
      </block>
